These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different nationalities: egyptian, argentine
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: volleyball, golf
The people use 2 different means of transport: train, jet-ski
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person driving the train##1
2. the argentine is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Nationality   | argentine    | egyptian |
| Sport         | golf | volleyball    |
| Transport     | train     | jet-ski      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: juice, milk
There are 2 different nationalities: egyptian, american
The people use 2 different means of transport: taxi, tram
1. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
2. the egyptian is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |
| Beverage      | milk  | juice   |
| Nationality   | american | egyptian  |
| Transport     | tram   | taxi |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: reading, card-games
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: disaster, comedy
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: water-polo, cricket
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is in an even position##4
2. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |
| Hobby         | reading   | card-games  |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | disaster  |
| Sport         | water-polo   | cricket |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-4::.
