The people prefer 2 different music-genres: hip-hop, gospel
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: ice-hockey, baseball
1. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |
| Hobby         | dancing    | rock-climbing    |
| Music-Genre   | gospel     | hip-hop      |
| Sport         | ice-hockey | baseball |

