.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-7::.
There 2 different types of food: eggplant, broccoli
The people have 2 different jobs:  photographer, manager
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: surfing, basketball
1. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the photographer##1
2. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is basketball##3
3. the person eating eggplant is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | broccoli | eggplant     |
| Job     | manager | photographer |
| Sport   | basketball | surfing    |

 #################################

 
