.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-14::.
There 2 different types of food: banana, pineapple
The people have 2 different hobbies: cooking, magic-tricks
2 different pets are kept: fish, goat
1. the owner of the goat is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person eating banana##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |
| Food    | pineapple | banana  |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks | cooking |
| Pet     | fish  | goat     |

