.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-15::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: fishing, magic-tricks
There are 2 different nationalities: japanese, dutch
2 different pets are kept: horse, guinea-pig
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
2. the japanese is on the left of the dutch##1
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks | fishing |
| Nationality   | japanese     | dutch     |
| Pet           | guinea-pig          | horse     |

